{"id":"gmickel-claude-marketplace-4wv","title":"Update Flow docs for RepoPrompt 1.5.62 CLI improvements","description":"RepoPrompt 1.5.62 adds:\n\n1. **-t flag for tab targeting** - Direct tab targeting instead of chaining `workspace tab`\n   - `rp-cli -w 3 -t \"TabName\" -e 'select get'`\n   - Builder returns tab UUID in output for follow-up commands\n\n2. **Progress notifications** - Shows progress during builder/chat to prevent timeout anxiety\n   - `[progress] context_builder: Starting...`\n   - Reduces need for our \"⚠️ WAIT 30s-5min\" warnings\n\n3. **prompt presets command** - List/select copy presets from CLI\n\nFiles to update:\n- plugins/flow/agents/context-scout.md (tab isolation section)\n- plugins/flow/skills/flow-plan-review/workflow.md\n- plugins/flow/skills/flow-plan-review/rp-cli-reference.md\n- plugins/flow/skills/flow-impl-review/workflow.md\n- plugins/flow/skills/flow-impl-review/rp-cli-reference.md\n- plugins/flow/skills/rp-explorer/cli-reference.md\n\nWait a few days for 1.5.62 to stabilize before updating.","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-06T00:59:47.112267+01:00","created_by":"gordon","updated_at":"2026-01-06T09:59:10.284423+01:00","closed_at":"2026-01-06T09:59:10.284423+01:00","close_reason":"All docs updated for RepoPrompt 1.5.62: -t flag, progress notifications, version requirement warnings"}
